## ğŸ”‘ Essential Environment Variables

| Variable | Required | Description | Example |
|----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| `OPENAI_API_KEY` | No* | For NPC AI responses | `sk-proj-...` |
| `ADMIN_PASSWORD` | No | Admin panel access | `secure123` |
| `NPC_AMBIENT` | No | Enable NPC ambient chat | `1` |
| `PORT` | No | Server port | `8080` |

*Optional - game works without it, but NPCs will use fallback responses

