## âœ… Quick Verification Checklist

After starting the game, verify these features work:

- [ ] **Loading Screen** - Shows "SOCIAL CREDIT" logo
- [ ] **Welcome Modal** - Username input appears
- [ ] **3D Scene** - Maze and ground render correctly
- [ ] **Movement** - WASD/arrows move avatar smoothly
- [ ] **Collision** - Can't walk through walls
- [ ] **Chat** - Can send messages in chat box
- [ ] **Minimap** - Shows in top-right corner
- [ ] **Score Display** - Shows in top-left corner
- [ ] **Context Menu** - Right-click shows menu
- [ ] **Notifications** - Appear when actions occur
- [ ] **FPS Counter** - Shows in top-left (small)
- [ ] **NPCs** - 6 NPCs visible and moving
- [ ] **Effects** - Ambient particles visible
- [ ] **Mobile** - Responsive on phone (if testing)

